 {"id":"franken_networkx-6t7","title":"Structural: k-edge augmentation, k-edge components, spectral bisection","description":"## Scope\nImplement 5 structural decomposition functions:\n- k_edge_augmentation(G, k, avail=None, weight=None, partial=False) — find minimum-weight set of edges to add to make G k-edge-connected. For k=1: connect components via minimum spanning forest of complement. For k=2: use ear decomposition to find bridges and add parallel paths. For general k: iterative approach. Returns list of (u,v) edges to add.\n- k_edge_components(G, k) — partition nodes into maximally k-edge-connected components. For k=1: connected_components. For k=2: biconnected_components minus bridges. General k: use max-flow.\n- k_edge_subgraphs(G, k) — yield subgraphs of k-edge-connected components (each is a subgraph induced by a component).\n- spectral_bisection(G, weight=None) — partition graph into two roughly equal parts using the sign of the Fiedler vector (second-smallest eigenvector of Laplacian). Nodes with positive Fiedler component go to one side, negative to the other. This is the basis of spectral clustering.\n- find_induced_nodes(G, s, d) — find all nodes at exactly distance d from node s via BFS. Returns set of nodes.\n\n## Dependencies\n- spectral_bisection depends on existing fiedler_vector implementation\n- k_edge_augmentation for k>=3 may depend on flow algorithms (already implemented)\n\n## Performance\n- k_edge_augmentation: O(k * max_flow_cost) for general k\n- spectral_bisection: O(n^2) for eigendecomposition, O(n+m) for sign partitioning\n- find_induced_nodes: O(n+m) BFS\n\n## Test Requirements\n- k_edge_augmentation: verify augmented graph has edge_connectivity >= k\n- k_edge_components: verify each component has internal edge connectivity >= k\n- spectral_bisection: verify partition is roughly balanced, cut size is reasonable\n- find_induced_nodes: verify all returned nodes are at exactly distance d\n- NX cross-validation on path, cycle, complete, and Petersen graphs","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-22T17:34:38.864656076Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-22T23:47:40.732277451Z","closed_at":"2026-03-22T23:47:40.731715185Z","close_reason":"Implemented k_edge_components, k_edge_subgraphs, spectral_bisection, find_induced_nodes, k_edge_augmentation.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["algorithms"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"franken_networkx-6t7","depends_on_id":"franken_networkx-ak4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-22T17:42:04.409020795Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
